NAME
	wizopt - set wizard options

ACCESS LEVEL
	apprentice or higher

DESCRIPTION
	Options only for wizards.

ARGUMENTS
        allcommune <on/off>  - See all communes as they happen.

	alwaysknown <on/off> - Mortal players always know your name.

	autopwd <on/off>     - Automatic display of the current working 
        [pwd on/off]           directory when you change it.

	autolinecmd <on/off> - Have the wizard line commands automatically
        [cmd on/off]	       available as comment. This means you can do
		               'someline xxx' instead of having to do
			       'line someline xxx' to speak on someline.

	timestamp <on/off>   - Show the wiz line with a time stamp.

SEE ALSO
	cd, commune, line, options
